title: Fritze (R.)
body: German botanist who collected plants in Madeira in 1879 and 1880. Ref.: Ueber die Farnvegetation der Insel Madeira (Jahresbericht der schlesischen Ges. fur vaterl. Kultur, (1881).

Madeira: Island where the plant collection took place.

1881: Year of publication of the report
